                    <div className="p-3 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 border border-orange-300 dark:border-orange-700 rounded">
                      <p className="text-sm font-medium text-orange-900 dark:text-orange-200">⏳ Waiting for Treasury</p>
                      <p className="text-xs text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-300 mt-1">
                        This application has been approved by treasury voting. Treasury needs to create the draft Pool Guarantee certificate before you can review and approve it.
                      </p>
                    </div>
